==English==
===Etymology===
[[Donald Duck]] + [[-ism]], from Norwegian [[Donaldismen]]
===Proper noun===
'''Donaldism'''
# fan culture that is found among fans of Disney comics and animated motion pictures and shorts. The word comes from "Donald Duck" and it was first used systematically and in writing by the Norwegian Jon Gisle, notably in his book Donaldismen from 1973.

